"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e5b95c11d4b69e700f586a5cd44c6e468b8284","tid":642501,"uid":16562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b09d92474bfb920027e7dc31e1160d48885d4782","tid":642501,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T03:23:33.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n從來未試過玩動作game 會煲成個夜晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有拎完雙刀, 後尾拎番d 符文攻擊出番晒d  經典連擊真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T03:57:04.000Z","msg":"無錯！！！<br />\n不過而家變左有CD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc4138f089ef2c818f3b86235555108f73b6531","tid":642501,"uid":33651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b09d92474bfb920027e7dc31e1160d48885d4782","tid":642501,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T03:23:33.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n從來未試過玩動作game 會煲成個夜晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有拎完雙刀, 後尾拎番d 符文攻擊出番晒d  經典連擊真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:16:28.000Z","msg":"d名都跟返"},{"pid":"a76fb2432c70ebe01e9f8af3ae015ab9f12a92b8","tid":642501,"uid":51275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T09:15:35.000Z","msg":"真係好撚正<br />\n我係由psp外傳1開始玩 <br />\n跟住玩埋ps2既1,2集<br />\n<br />\n睇住奎頭由一個超級燥底人變左個竟然識放下層刀既成熟大叔真係好感慨<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無人同我一樣 次次見到奎頭有朋友一齊既時候會好開心<br />\n因為集集大部分時間都係自已一個既冒險<br />\n小數出現過既朋友/隊友都好快死<br />\n之前玩第二集 玩到奎頭唔小心殺左自已個同伴果下真係sad撚到<br />\n<br />\n今集同個仔全程一齊 見到佢咁錫個仔真係好開心<br />\n<br />\nsorry for1999 但我爆完機之後個心情仲未平伏到 好想快d出新集<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0d5429372c3ec57f7971fa69b7aa262628822d","tid":642501,"uid":64865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74abc58dae1e59561a32960caf1ed717aa9ff693","tid":642501,"uid":106019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T23:27:35.000Z","msg":"最後講個仔幅畫係咩意思？會殺老豆？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T09:38:16.000Z","msg":"兩睇<br />\n可能係臨死前訓響 loki 腳度"},{"pid":"e4b8ebe5963dde4b774d7f5527b27e1f5d335edd","tid":642501,"uid":64865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T09:41:51.000Z","msg":"爆咗機返屋企訓覺<br />\n有第二集伏線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩完希臘三部曲會唔會有北歐三部曲<br />\n諸神黃昏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317e3a9d48208572ae1de0974ce767c7db27e949","tid":642501,"uid":38540,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T09:49:57.000Z","msg":"未睇過咁垃圾既game評<br />\n成篇野都冇提過遊戲性 音樂 畫面 <br />\n淨係狂loop回憶回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e48109d5e84a90762374dfd33a5ddee36bf18f6","tid":642501,"uid":6211,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"317e3a9d48208572ae1de0974ce767c7db27e949","tid":642501,"uid":38540,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T09:49:57.000Z","msg":"未睇過咁垃圾既game評<br />\n成篇野都冇提過遊戲性 音樂 畫面 <br />\n淨係狂loop回憶回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T09:51:56.000Z","msg":"感想=g